
---

## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Terraform local state
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Terraform working directory
**/.terraform/*
**/.terraform.lock.hcl

# Variable files (often contain secrets)
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json

# If you want to commit safe tfvars, remove the lines above and ignore only secrets:
# **/*.auto.tfvars
# **/*.auto.tfvars.json

# Override files
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# CLI config files
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

# IDE / OS junk
.vscode/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Disabled backend files (keep out of git)
**/*.disabled